{"type":null,"faqId":22418,"title":"DLNA 如何使用？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in;}\n.p1{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.19722222in;margin-left:0.31527779in;margin-top:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.36805555in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<a name=\"set3_p1\"></a><span>方式一：通过华为盒子，将手机上的本地视频推送到电视上播放。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1  </span><span>将手机和华为盒子连接至同一个家庭网络。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2  </span><span>在手机上下载DLNA客户端软件。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3  </span><span>在手机上启动DLNA客户端，根据界面指引，共享或推送手机上的视频到电视上播放。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>方式二：共享 Window7 电脑上的流媒体文件，在电视上播放。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1  </span><span>将 Window7 电脑和华为盒子连接至同一个家庭网络。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2  </span><span>在电脑上打开 Windows Media Player，选择“</span><span class=\"s2\">媒体流</span><span>”依次选择“</span><span class=\"s2\">打开媒体流</span><span>”、“</span><span class=\"s2\">允许远程控制我的播放器</span><span>”、“</span><span class=\"s2\">自动允许设备播放我的媒体</span><span>”，根据界面指引完成共享操作。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3  </span><span>进入华为盒子“</span><span class=\"s2\">应用 &gt;</span><span> </span><span class=\"s2\">媒体中心</span><span>”，找到电脑共享的流媒体文件，点击即可播放。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":245,"faqType":"多屏互动","useful":3,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"6298","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Screen-Sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1428628513000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M330","visitedTimes":150,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":n